{"tid":2032141,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"無知一問，其實游擊對你哋嚟講係咩意思","createTime":"2020-05-24T01:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T23:48:53.000Z","uid":161174,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfea7857d45151a2c5579e0330e6b6d3b15d856","tid":2032141,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:43:21.000Z","msg":"唔好介意我多口問一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我發現我本身嘅理解，同手足們所諗嘅好似有少少出入<br />\n其實我見手足們一直都有話打游擊<br />\n<br />\n手足們：<br />\n到時候先公報時間地點，然後就等集合多人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(其實出過幾次，我覺得得集合用咗太多時間。狗屋就係隔離，我哋睇到班狗都會mon到。而且手足們唔會長時間mon住文宣，變咗班狗到咗，手足都未到，咁好似已經冇咗游擊嘅意義。)</span><br />\n而且要等多人先行動<br />\n<br />\n我：<br />\n我個人印象中嘅嘅游擊係小隊形式<br />\n而且打完對方一嘢就即閃，冇咩必要戀戰"},{"pid":"bed7599cd620a23c28e67e77be91f4ffd6eff454","tid":2032141,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:43:51.000Z","msg":"實施游擊戰的原因<br />\n<br />\n游擊戰必定是<span style=\"color: red;\">敵強我弱</span>，敵方強大到我方不能用其他距離戰法與之相對抗，或用距離戰法我方損失太大，大到我方無以為繼，這時就只能用 正因為敵方強大，擁有大型部隊，所以游擊戰多是在弱方的國土上進行，也因弱方熟悉該區之地形。<br />\n<br />\n游擊戰的特性<br />\n<br />\n游擊戰一般來說沒有標準的制服和武器，通常是以能自給自足的<span style=\"color: red;\">小單位如伍或班(排)</span>，利用地形作為掩護，在自己所熟悉的地形裡四處出擊，用少量部隊在一個點上創造局部優勢，也就是雖然你有一萬人我只有一千人，但我用時間可以慢慢消滅你的力量。總之就是<span style=\"color: red;\">零敲零打，讓敵人一開始不會損失很多，但這個數字會慢慢累積</span>，直到敵人軍隊<span style=\"color: red;\">士氣崩潰</span>、糧食不足時，再發動致命的總攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n戰術層面<br />\n<br />\n游擊戰<span style=\"color: red;\">因兵力少而火力弱，很難獨立定點地進行長時間作戰，必須有當地民眾提供物資、情報等資源</span>，並積極創造條件，利用天時及地形並搭配陷阱，以機動力及隱蔽性主動出擊，遭遇強大敵人時化整為零，消耗敵人戰力、拖延敵人行動、誤導敵人方向，形成敵人心理上極大壓力才可能致勝。"},{"pid":"a2f8b95d491a5ec887a065b06245435f9fc97e53","tid":2032141,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa7233df7e283be231e9d8c51db7311fc3c7d7f","tid":2032141,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2f8b95d491a5ec887a065b06245435f9fc97e53","tid":2032141,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:56:43.000Z","msg":"矮仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba9b9ced3287d39d9414421b49a4867b46cc163","tid":2032141,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa7233df7e283be231e9d8c51db7311fc3c7d7f","tid":2032141,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2f8b95d491a5ec887a065b06245435f9fc97e53","tid":2032141,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:56:43.000Z","msg":"矮仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"去Sogo 行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee67ea1dd52041e047ccdefd66b2b06169707a7","tid":2032141,"uid":263618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:02:29.000Z","msg":"i just know without 避彈衣打條春咩<br />\n唔記得狗會用實彈？<br />\n唔記得熊仔餅手足無左個腎？"},{"pid":"b0d9224f6bc8c830e3dc9e7696b233e4c11d6f91","tid":2032141,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee67ea1dd52041e047ccdefd66b2b06169707a7","tid":2032141,"uid":263618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:02:29.000Z","msg":"i just know without 避彈衣打條春咩<br />\n唔記得狗會用實彈？<br />\n唔記得熊仔餅手足無左個腎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:24:59.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146cd138e45d67c7b53cab557e1079c14b8c41d5","tid":2032141,"uid":116614,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:33:28.000Z","msg":"出擊d咩?<br />\n搖旗吶喊笑班狗,然後同佢賽跑比人㩒低?<br />\n定引狗做無後果行為令身邊人一齊食?<br />\n我真心唔明漫無目的出嚟行街係咩意思<br />\n畫面靚d?定引發慘劇等中共可憐?"},{"pid":"3af6612724079046ee3604ee432b11fbe9249ae9","tid":2032141,"uid":116614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"致命嘅總攻擊係咩?2百萬人係水炮車前面坐低?<br />\n定係到場睇連登tg群決定?"},{"pid":"8a218e13e3d79575b8288e8249bb6f6433e3d27a","tid":2032141,"uid":37489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"與其話係遊擊 不如話係情報差異"},{"pid":"bdbfbff85a4950fb64cfcd208203bc1cc2bc5ba6","tid":2032141,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"db9ae86e735d03cc50c226fc5ded85ca357a5b42","tid":2032141,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a218e13e3d79575b8288e8249bb6f6433e3d27a","tid":2032141,"uid":37489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"與其話係遊擊 不如話係情報差異"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:22:47.000Z","msg":"都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且喺現場等人嚟都冇咩用<br />\n班mon post狗一早嚟曬"},{"pid":"137b1e7af58b2713ac6c44544a0e533feb028708","tid":2032141,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"9fe611f570041f31276ecf1412ef126c9f9c0bae","tid":2032141,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:22:30.000Z","msg":"聚2000人係到鳩叫 10隻狗嚟 就跑到好似打仗咁"},{"pid":"ea9172d0a2039c8873580146e2e834318928b0d4","tid":2032141,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fe611f570041f31276ecf1412ef126c9f9c0bae","tid":2032141,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:22:30.000Z","msg":"聚2000人係到鳩叫 10隻狗嚟 就跑到好似打仗咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:09:54.000Z","msg":"我唔係想批評啲咩<br />\n始終雙方裝備都有好大差距<br />\n<br />\n我覺得敵強我弱情況下，用游擊係好<br />\n但又覺得大家所做嘅游擊，同我印象中嘅有出入"},{"pid":"4d92c2acb8892a93384f1aaa5f82d0988b